channel.title: Please help with this error
channel.description:
Please help with this error, i shut off my server to compile, turn it back on and this happend
[code]Satan's Isle : Second Pk source , is ONLINE ! Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: " 2" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1422) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:29) at server.main(server.java:28) [/code]
Then it all screwes up and you cant log in
